description:
As Gods creations, the longing of our hearts can only be satisfied by His love.

In the Scottish Mission, a record number of Adventists gathered to pray and worship the Lord, in search of spiritual revival. 

The Operation Enduring Faith event was a testimony to a church hungry for God.  

Learn more on ANN Weekly and find more news stories on our website, adventist.news.
fulltitle: 500 People Attend a Revival Event by an Adventist Church in Scotland
